OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAfter a
OL,6,Fbright and warm evening, low cloud
OL,7,Fwill move back in overnight to bring
OL,8,Fmist and hill fog in some areas.
OL,9,FStaying dry and warm overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FLow cloud will burn back
OL,12,Fduring the morning to bring sunny
OL,13,Fskies. Feeling very warm in the
OL,14,Fsunshine and light winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,17,FStaying dry and increasingly hot
OL,18,Fthrough the outlook. Plenty of strong
OL,19,Fsunshine and light winds, with some
OL,20,Fwarm nights too.
